      replay: `<header class="page-head"><div><h1>运行回放与评价</h1><p id="replaySubtitle">正在读取本次仿真记录…</p></div><button class="button" id="refreshReplay">刷新记录</button></header><div class="page-body split"><section class="pane"><div class="timeline"><button class="button" id="replayToggle">▶</button><time id="replayStart">00:00</time><input id="replayRange" type="range" min="0" max="0" value="0" style="flex:1" aria-label="回放时间轴"><time id="replayEnd">00:00</time></div><div class="pane-title" style="margin-top:22px"><h2 id="replayTrainTitle">速度回放</h2><span>500 ms 采样</span></div><div class="chart" style="height:300px"><svg id="replayChart" viewBox="0 0 800 280" preserveAspectRatio="none"><text x="400" y="140" text-anchor="middle" fill="#73858e">暂无回放数据</text></svg></div><div class="command-feedback" id="replayFrame">等待记录</div></section><aside class="pane"><div class="eyebrow">安全操作评分</div><div class="score" id="replayScore">—<small> / 100</small></div><div class="kv"><span>当前场景</span><b id="replayScenario">—</b></div><div class="kv"><span>采样帧数</span><b id="replayFrameCount">0</b></div><div class="kv"><span>事件总数</span><b id="replayEventCount">0</b></div><p style="color:var(--muted);margin-top:24px">评分当前按严重事件扣分，是基础评价口径；停车精度、平稳性和能耗评分将在评价器接入后展示。</p></aside></div>`
